This directory contains modified code that is originally from ESPS. A version
of ESPS source code is available from the following web site.

  http://ldc.upenn.edu/myl/esps60.6.linmac.src.tgz

ESPS was originally developed by Entropic Inc., which was later acquired by
Microsoft in 1999.  Eventually, the source code was released under the BSD
license by KTH.

  http://www.speech.kth.se/esps/esps.zip


